{
  "stem": "1160.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you are in the middle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my brother is going to roll to you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm from this side to you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whoever gets to you first has to take a bite from the bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got us some food this way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the-- and then we told him, don't you dare tell your mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't you dare tell your mother what we did this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But because 1, 2. 3, the slice of bread was gone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he-- he-- he liked the game very much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wonder if he remembers it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He liked the game very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was fascinated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he didn't eat too much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he had no problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He just went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we says, don't you dare tell your mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, a child, he told the mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He comes back-- [LAUGHS] --again with a bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this time she's watching.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But this happened a few times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We could give-- get the bread from him like this with a game.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And again, sometimes the mother came out and says, you bad children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You-- I know you are tricking him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you're just taking the food away from him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I guess she didn't mind it so much, because she saw that we are hungry, and-- and end of the war, and showing this picture.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So probably, you know, we should have a good impression, you know, something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I-- I'm just speculating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A matter of fact, they-- the-- our leader, who was-- we picked, you know, a leader of the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Group.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He is the one who was-- somebody was talking, somebody came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's the one who was-- they were talking to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We called him the [NON-ENGLISH], a Weinberger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Weinberger.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
